code: /**  * Check if a service definition matches.  */ default boolean matches(ServiceDefinition other) {     if (this.equals(other)) {         return true.     }     return getPort() == other.getPort() && StringHelper.matches(getName(), other.getName()) && StringHelper.matches(getId(), other.getId()) && StringHelper.matches(getHost(), other.getHost()). }
